.name
Patch
.author
Larry Wall 
.source
Includes source in C.
.description
Two independent ports of the very useful Unix utility "patch", which
applies context diffs to text files to automatically update them.  Patch
version 1.3 was ported to the Amiga by Rick Coupland and patch version 2.0
was ported by Johan Widen.  
